3省5个监狱共确诊555例，司法部谈疫情细节漏洞。
A total of 555 cases were identified in five prisons in three provinces, and the Ministry of Justice addressed the details of the outbreak.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 林平2月26日上午，国务院应对新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情联防联控机制举行新闻发布会，介绍《关于政法机关依法保障疫情防控期间复工复产的意见》有关情况。
Peng Pai journalist Lin Ping held a press conference on February 26 morning to introduce the Opinions on the Legal Protection of Resumption of Work during the Prevention and Control of Coronavirus Infection by the New Coronavirus Infection.
近期监狱病例激增所致，疫情如何在监狱传播？目前治疗情况如何？司法部副部长熊选国介绍，截至2月25日，全国3个省5个监狱发生了感染疫情，湖北、浙江、山东5个监狱共确诊病例555例，疑似19例，重症4例。
As of February 25, 555 cases had been diagnosed in five prisons in Hubei, Zhejiang and Shandong provinces, with 19 cases suspected and 4 cases of serious illness, said Xiong Xiang, vice minister of justice.
到目前为止，没有发生监狱在押罪犯感染新冠肺炎死亡的病例。
To date, there have been no cases of death from neonatal pneumonia among prisoners in prison.
全国其他监狱除了这5所之外，没有发生罪犯感染疫情。
In all but five of the other prisons in the country, there were no outbreaks of infection among prisoners.
“监狱疫情传播确实反映了监狱管理和防控疫情工作中存在的漏洞。
"The spread of the epidemic in prisons does reflect the gaps in prison management and prevention and control efforts.
”熊选国直言，首先是思想重视不够，比如湖北武汉女子监狱，它距离武汉肺科医院大概不到100米，干警上下班和肺科医院的病人是同一个公交站，在全面实现封闭前，可能已经导致病毒输入”。
For example, Wuhan Women's Prison in Hubei Province, which is less than 100 meters away from Wuhan Lung Hospital, where patients from police commutes and lung hospitals share the same bus station and may have caused the virus to enter before the closure is fully realized.
其次是严格管理不到位。
Secondly, strict management is not in place.
熊选国举例说，湖北汉津监狱、浙江十里丰监狱、山东任城监狱，这些监狱发生疫情都是由于个别干警不如实报告接触到湖北疫区的人员，隔离不彻底，进而导致输入性病例。
Xiong selected countries as an example, Hubei Han Jin prison, Zhejiang 10 Li Feng prison, Shandong Ren Cheng prison, these prison outbreaks are due to a few cases of underreporting of contact with Hubei epidemic areas by individual dry police officers, resulting in incomplete isolation, leading to imported cases.
“疫情在监狱传播，充分暴露出这些地方思想认识不深刻，干警管理不严格，防控措施落实不及时，工作中存在严重形式主义、官僚主义问题。
"The spread of the epidemic in prisons has fully exposed the lack of deep ideological understanding in these places, the lax management of dry police, the slow implementation of prevention and control measures, and the existence of serious formalism and bureaucracy in the work.
”熊选国指出，监狱发生疫情教训十分深刻，全国监狱系统充分认识监狱疫情防控工作的特殊性、复杂性、严峻性和极端重要性，严格全封闭管理、严格落实、严格责任，严格问责，杜绝监狱管理漏洞，坚决遏制监狱疫情蔓延扩散，同时要全力做好救助工作，罪犯出现发热或者呼吸道症状，第一时间要进行隔离观察，对确诊罪犯要与社会其他人员一样，同等及时的予以救治，有11名患者已经治愈。
The country's prison system is fully aware of the special, complex, severe and extremely important nature of the prevention and control of prison epidemics, strictly closed management, strict implementation, strict responsibility and strict accountability, eliminate loopholes in prison administration and resolutely curb the spread of the epidemic.
